Name: Matchsticks - Coffee Break Club
About the game: A puzzle game with matchsticks where your mind will be constantly challenged after each level. Move, add or remove sticks to obtain the correct answer before you run out of moves. One puzzle may contain more than one solution. No time, no score, no pressure! Take your time at each level. 60 carefully selected puzzles. Practice your memory, logical and spatial thinking. 3 beautiful and original themes to be selected Original soundtrack exclusive to this game, by Tatyana Jacques Coding and development by the programmer Alexander Froelich
